<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Σαραπάμμων Θα-

    <lb n="2"/>ήσει τῇ <expan>ἀδελ<ex cert="high">φῇ</ex></expan> χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>διεπεμψάμην σοι 

    <lb n="4"/>οἴνου κεράμιον διὰ 

    <lb n="5"/>Π<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>τᾶ τινος ναυτι-

    <lb n="6"/>κοῦ, ὅπερ εἰ ἐκομί-

    <lb n="7"/>σω δήλωσόν μοι. 

    <lb n="8"/>εἰ γὰρ οὐκ ἠνέχθη 

    <lb n="9"/>σοι, γενοῦ εἰς τὸ γνα-

    <lb n="10"/>φεῖον Ἡρακλείου καὶ 

    <lb n="11"/>μάθε εἰ παρετέ-

    <lb n="12"/>θη αὐτοῖς καὶ δέξαι 

    <lb n="13"/>αὐτό. γεν<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οῦ</supplied> δὲ καὶ ε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἰ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="14"/>τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸ</supplied> ἐργαστ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ήριον</supplied> 

    <lb n="15"/>καὶ μάθε <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">εἰ ἐν ἀσφα</supplied>-

    <lb n="16"/>λεῖ ἐστι κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ ε</supplied>ἰ ἔρρω-

    <lb n="17"/>ται ἡ ἐν τῷ αἰθρίῳ 

    <lb n="18"/>κειμένη μεγάλη 

    <lb n="19"/>θυ<hi rend="diaeresis">ΐ</hi>α, καὶ πῶς ἔχεις 

    <lb n="20"/>γράψον μοι. ἔμελ-

    <lb n="21"/>λον γὰρ ἀνελθεῖν, καὶ 

    <lb n="22"/><hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>περθέμην ἔστ᾽ ἂν 

    <lb n="23"/>μάθω πότερον <app type="BL"><lem resp="3.138">ἐρά-

    <lb n="24"/>ϊσας</lem><rdg>ἐρᾷ <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>σᾶϲ</rdg></app> ἢ οὐ, καὶ εἰ χρεία 

    <lb n="25"/>ἐστὶ τοῦ με ἀνελθεῖν. 

    <lb n="26"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε <expan>εὔχομ<ex cert="high">αι</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="27"/><expan>Χοί<ex cert="high">ακ</ex></expan> <num value="24">κδ</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="28"/>εἰς τὸ Ἰσεῖον ὥστε Θαήσει <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> <expan>Σαραπάμμω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear><ex cert="high">ος</ex></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.28998" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.28998" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="200" notBefore="101" type="textDate">II</date></p></div><div n="meta.28998" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Tag: 20. (21.) Dez.</p></div><div n="meta.28998" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">1488</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">28998</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">12</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">1488</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;12;1488" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.28998" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.28998" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><geogName cert="high" full="yes" type="nome">Oxyrhynchites</geogName>, <geogName cert="high" full="yes" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>